channel.title: Run Server Error (RSCD V25)
channel.description:
i get this error when i try to run the server: java.io.FileNotFoundException: log\event.log (Den angivne sti blev ikke fundet) at java.io.FileOutputStream.open(Native Method) at java.io.FileOutputStream.<init>(Unknown Source) at java.io.FileOutputStream.<init>(Unknown Source) at com.rscd.util.Logger.<clinit>(Logger.java:22) at com.rscd.Server.main(Server.java:46) Tryk på en vilkårlig tast for at fortsætte . . .
- It says that it can't find the event.log file, but it's in the right position?
